WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.662
Consider a scenario where a critical global project is failing.

00:00:04.662 --> 00:00:09.323
The launch is delayed, the budget is bleeding, and the

00:00:09.323 --> 00:00:13.985
cross-functional team is frustrated. The practical payoff of handling this

00:00:13.985 --> 00:00:18.646
correctly is the difference between a stalled career and transformative

00:00:18.646 --> 00:00:23.308
leadership. When facing a complex, undefined challenge at headquarters, an

00:00:23.308 --> 00:00:27.969
average manager might react by assigning blame or enforcing rigid

00:00:27.969 --> 00:00:32.630
rules. A transformative leader, however, engineers an environment for active,

00:00:32.630 --> 00:00:37.292
self-built understanding to solve the root cause.
